{
  "stem": "21626.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, it was all so unjust.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But at least we had a little bit which was our own.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And as Auntie Milla was expecting her first baby, we knew knew a two-roomed flat couldn't house five of us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But-- so we were already there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the only facility for cooking was one little burner, gas burner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then there was a little steel-- well, it wasn't steel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was copper.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was iron or something-- little gas oven, portable oven.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I just turned it on and put my head in it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I wanted to commit suicide.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I just felt I couldn't cope.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But luckily, the only girlfriend I made in the class felt that I was really, really upset.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I-- I left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I haven't said anything to anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But I just sort of rushed out of school, out of class.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And she came after me and stopped me being successful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I was very glad, very glad I wasn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But it was so hard, you know, to come to terms with that sort of treatment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then when I went for the first time to my hometown, that again was-- it took an awful lot of courage to walk down the streets which formed my, you know, my childhood, towards the house in which we lived.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Nobody knew I had come, and nobody recognized me immediately.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I went-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --to the staircase which led to our large flat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And you know, before I left, I wrote.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "It was a silly thing to do, but probably a natural thing to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I wrote in my childish hand on the wall of the lavatory, goodbye, my lavatory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And father, in one of his many letters, said that they were having the whole flat decorated.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
